wnership and student enrollment. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/role-feature-matrix.md:14:| Mentor | `My Mentees`, `Queue History`, `Calendar / Timetable`, faculty profile button | Session login and `role-context`; `GET /api/academic/bootstrap`; mentor-scoped task and meeting creation; `student-shell` and `risk-explorer` require active-run + student scope | `mentee-detail`, `student-history`, `student-shell`, and `risk-explorer` are reached from mentee cards and history links, not from top-level nav | Mentor UI is narrow, but indirect student drilldowns remain first-class routes. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/role-feature-matrix.md:15:| HoD | `Department`, `Queue History`, `Calendar / Timetable`, unlock-review actions in the queue, faculty profile button | Session login and `role-context`; `GET /api/academic/bootstrap`; HoD proof bundle endpoints; governed request list/create; faculty profile reads with department/branch overlap checks; HOD-scoped offering and student access checks; `student-shell` and `risk-explorer` require active-run + student scope | `unlock-review` is not a top-level nav item but is opened from queue actions or direct hashes; `faculty-profile` can target any faculty only when the overlap check passes | HoD is the only academic role with dedicated proof-summary/bundle/courses/faculty/students/reassessments reads. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/role-feature-matrix.md:16:| SYSTEM_ADMIN | `#/admin` overview, proof dashboard, faculties, students, faculty members, requests, history, and canonical proof hierarchy drilldowns | All `/api/admin/*` families, proof sandbox routes, session restore/logout/role-context, `faculty-profile` self/admin/HOD read path, `student-shell`, `risk-explorer`, and preferences | `#/admin/faculties/:.../batches/:...` is the canonical proof route; `#/admin/history` is the hidden-records surface; search can route into students, faculty, and requests without using the visible tabs | `SystemAdminSessionBoundary` blocks the workspace unless the active session role is `SYSTEM_ADMIN`, even if the user is logged in under another grant. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/role-feature-matrix.md:20:- `canAccessPage()` is a client-side gate only. It keeps the academic router from staying on a disallowed page, but it does not replace backend auth.\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/role-feature-matrix.md:23:- `requireRole()` is the first backend gate on the protected routes. It checks the active grant only.\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/role-feature-matrix.md:32:- `student-history`, `student-shell`, and `risk-explorer` are cross-cutting routes reached from student cards, mentee cards, queue rows, and proof controls.\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/role-feature-matrix.md:33:- `unlock-review` is reachable from queue actions and direct hashes, even though it is not a top-level sidebar item.\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/role-feature-matrix.md:34:- `#/admin/proof-dashboard` and the canonical proof hierarchy route are route-level entry points, not visible top tabs.\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/role-feature-matrix.md:35:- `#/admin/history` is a hidden-records workspace, but admin search can still surface requests from that section.\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/role-feature-matrix.md:43:- `student-shell` and `risk-explorer` are easy to reach indirectly, but their server-side scope checks are stricter than the route names imply.\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/feature-registry.md:7:| Public portal chooser and hash routing | Bootstrap / portal entry | `src/App.tsx`, `src/portal-entry.tsx`, `src/portal-routing.ts` | [`04-feature-atoms/public-portal-chooser-and-routing.md`](../04-feature-atoms/public-portal-chooser-and-routing.md) |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/feature-registry.md:9:| Academic role switching and route sync | Bootstrap / academic role surface | `src/App.tsx`, `src/academic-workspace-route-helpers.ts`, `air-mentor-api/src/modules/session.ts`, `src/academic-workspace-topbar.tsx` | [`04-feature-atoms/academic-role-switching-and-route-sync.md`](../04-feature-atoms/academic-role-switching-and-route-sync.md) |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/feature-registry.md:10:| Academic bootstrap snapshot and proof playback | Bootstrap / academic proof data | `air-mentor-api/src/modules/academic-bootstrap-routes.ts`, `src/App.tsx`, `src/api/client.ts`, `src/repositories.ts` | [`04-feature-atoms/academic-bootstrap-snapshot-and-proof-playback.md`](../04-feature-atoms/academic-bootstrap-snapshot-and-proof-playback.md) |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:3:Pass: `route-map-pass`\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:9:- Frontend routing is hash-based at the portal level.\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:10:- The academic workspace uses internal page state, not React Router.\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:11:- The sysadmin workspace uses structured hash deep links and canonical proof-route helpers.\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:18:| `#/` | `PortalRouterApp` -> `PortalEntryScreen` in [`src/App.tsx`](../../src/App.tsx) and [`src/portal-entry.tsx`](../../src/portal-entry.tsx) | Public chooser | Top-level portal landing page. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:19:| `#/app` | `PortalRouterApp` -> `OperationalApp` in [`src/App.tsx`](../../src/App.tsx) | Authenticated academic portal | Any `#/app/*` hash also resolves here. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:20:| `#/admin` | `PortalRouterApp` -> `SystemAdminApp` -> `SystemAdminLiveApp` in [`src/App.tsx`](../../src/App.tsx) and [`src/system-admin-app.tsx`](../../src/system-admin-app.tsx) | Authenticated `SYSTEM_ADMIN` portal | Any `#/admin/*` hash also resolves here. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:24:These are route states inside `OperationalApp`, not URL path segments. Entry navigation comes from the role-specific sidebar, the top bar, and cross-link handlers in [`src/App.tsx`](../../src/App.tsx).\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:40:| `faculty-profile` | `FacultyProfilePage` | Cross-cutting route | Sidebar faculty-profile button; `handleOpenStudentProfile` may route here for mentor/self profile views. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:41:| `student-history` | `StudentHistoryPage` | Cross-cutting route | Student cards, mentee cards, queue items, history cross-links. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:42:| `student-shell` | `StudentShellPage` | Cross-cutting route | Student history cross-link, student drawer, proof controls. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:43:| `risk-explorer` | `RiskExplorerPage` | Cross-cutting route | Student history cross-link, student drawer, proof controls. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:45:Role gating is enforced by [`src/academic-workspace-route-helpers.ts`](../../src/academic-workspace-route-helpers.ts):\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:58:| `#/admin/overview` | `SystemAdminLiveApp` overview workspace | `SYSTEM_ADMIN` | Default admin landing route. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:59:| `#/admin/proof-dashboard` | Proof dashboard workspace | `SYSTEM_ADMIN` | Proof-scoped admin surface. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:60:| `#/admin/students` | Student registry workspace | `SYSTEM_ADMIN` | Registry list route. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:61:| `#/admin/students/:studentId` | Student detail workspace | `SYSTEM_ADMIN` | Direct entity drilldown. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:62:| `#/admin/faculty-members` | Faculty registry workspace | `SYSTEM_ADMIN` | Registry list route. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:63:| `#/admin/faculty-members/:facultyMemberId` | Faculty detail workspace | `SYSTEM_ADMIN` | Direct entity drilldown. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:64:| `#/admin/requests` | Governed requests workspace | `SYSTEM_ADMIN` and some `HOD`-backed flows | List route. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:65:| `#/admin/requests/:requestId` | Request detail workspace | `SYSTEM_ADMIN` and some `HOD`-backed flows | Direct entity drilldown. |\\naudit-map/15-final-maps/route-map.md:66:| `#/a