+- Confidence: high.
+
+### T-005: Accessibility and UX density under real data
+- Surface or workflow: modal dialogs, proof launchers, proof summary strips, admin tabs, and the dense proof/workspace rail.
+- Existing tests: `tests/system-admin-accessibility-contracts.test.tsx`, `tests/ui-primitives-accessibility-contracts.test.tsx`, `tests/ui-primitives-modal.test.tsx`, `tests/system-admin-ui.test.ts`, `tests/proof-surface-shell.test.tsx`, `tests/proof-surface-launcher.test.tsx`, `tests/academic-proof-summary-strip.test.tsx`, `tests/faculty-profile-proof.test.tsx`, `tests/system-admin-proof-dashboard-workspace.test.tsx`.
